aig-david-expresses-interest-in-working-with-usher-it-would-be-one-to-say-we-ticked-that-box-3822142">克雷格·大卫 (Craig David) 表达了与亚瑟 (Usher) 合作的兴趣：“这将是一个说我们勾选了那个框”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
